title: 2.5 bedrooms and 2.5 bath townhouse
posting_body: ['2 Story, 2.5 bedrooms and 2.5 bath townhouse with 1 car attached garage', 'Rare opportunity.', 'This is not your typical rental.', 'This rental really has it all.', 'Freshly painted, new flooring and updated unit.', 'There is an office space off the master bedroom.', 'In unit washer and dryer.', 'Central heating and A/C.', '2nd bathroom has walk in closet and master bathroom has linen closet along with two largest closets.', '2.5 bathrooms.', 'Powder room is downstairs.', 'Upstairs is 2nd bathroom with a tub and master bathroom with shower.', 'Kitchen includes gas range, dishwasher, microwave, and fridge.', 'High ceiling in living room with skylight.', 'Townhouse has its own entrance front patio area (pictured)', 'Attached large one car garage.', 'One additional parking space outside of unit.', 'Convenient location.', 'Close to shopping center in Orland along with many restaurants and other businesses.', 'Metra is only minutes away.', 'Very quite building.', 'Located in single family home neighborhood.', 'Park along with creek within walking distance.', 'Available now.', 'No pets per HOA.', 'One year lease term.', 'Looking for longer term tenants.', 'Credit check and background check required.', 'Min credit score of 690.', 'Income min and verification', 'HOA (trash, sewer, snow removal, exterior maintenance) included in rent.', 'Not included in rent: water, gas, and electricity.', 'Unit is not furnished.', 'Security deposit is $3,150', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Broker Owned Property', 'Applications available on Zillow.', 'Please submit showing requests here: https://forms.gle/AXWjmvxnz1Gp8erY7']
